sub_fields.label: Tile Content
sub_fields.name: tile_content
sub_fields.instructions: Numbers are automatically generated inside the tiles.

sub_fields.label: Text with Icons Rows
sub_fields.name: text_with_icons_rows
sub_fields.instructions:
This section contains a red background, with all text being white by default. 
Please ensure any uploaded icons are also white.

sub_fields.label: Note
sub_fields.message: The content for this block can be managed in the Site Settings

sub_fields.label: Map Address
sub_fields.name: map_address
sub_fields.instructions: Override address for the map. Defaults to Revo Fitness [Gym Name] if not set, which may not appear in Google Maps correctly.

sub_fields.label: Content
sub_fields.name: content
sub_fields.instructions: This content will be placed above the cards.

sub_fields.label: Video Link
sub_fields.name: video_link
sub_fields.instructions: Upload your video to the media library, then copy the file URL and paste it here.

sub_fields.label: iframe
sub_fields.name: iframe
sub_fields.instructions: Paste your iFrame video here. PLEASE NOTE: Change the width and height values to 100%.

sub_fields.label: Scrolling Text
sub_fields.name: scrolling_text
sub_fields.default_value: To the person with their favourite squat rack, we get you

sub_fields.label: Message
sub_fields.message: Populated by gyms that have the studio box ticked.

sub_fields.label: Form ID
sub_fields.name: form_id
sub_fields.instructions: Paste the form ID here from FORMS in the left admin menu.
